 <script>
 // HOUSTON BOTTOM LEFT CORNER FLY-IN
 jQuery(document).ready(function() {
     if (window.location.href.indexOf("/product/") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/account/") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/basket") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/checkout/") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/search") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("/order-form") > -1) {
 
     } else {
         function houstonHelpFlyIn() {
             days = 365;
             myDate = new Date();
             myDate.setTime(myDate.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             document.cookie = 'houstonHelpFlyIn=Accepted; expires=' + myDate.toGMTString();
         }
         var cookie = document.cookie.split(';')
             .map(function(x) {
                 return x.trim().split('=');
             })
             .filter(function(x) {
                 return x[0] === 'houstonHelpFlyIn';
             })
             .pop();
         if (cookie && cookie[1] === 'Accepted') {
             $("#houstonHelp").hide();
         } else {
             $('#houstonHelp #closeHoustonHelp').on('click', function() {
                 houstonHelpFlyIn();
                 return false;
             });
             $('#houstonHelp #closeHoustonHelp').click(function() {
                 $('#houstonHelp').removeClass('fly-in-from-left');
             });
             $(window).load(function() {
                 setTimeout(function() {
                     $('#houstonHelp').addClass('fly-in-from-left');
                 }, 1500);
             });
         }
     }
 });
 </script>

   </script>
   <script>
    var openId = qs('openId')+'';
 	var scrolltop = qs('scrolltop')+'';
 	if(openId != '') {
 		$(window).load(function(){
 			setTimeout(function() {
 				$('#'+openId).click().touchstart();
 			},1);
 		})
 	}
 	if(scrolltop == 'true') {
 		$(window).scrollTop();
 	}
   </script>
